items.title: OpenAI’s $3 billion deal with AI coding startup Windsurf collapses, as Google swoops in for licensing deal
items.description: Windsurf will continue to operate as an independent company

items.title: California pampers its chickens and Americans pay the price, Trump argues in new DOJ lawsuit
items.description: The DOJ lawsuit blames California's animal welfare laws for soaring egg prices. Activists cry bird flu.

items.title: Markets wobble after Trump threatens Canada with 35% tariff over alleged ‘flow of Fentanyl’
items.description: The S&P 500 fell 0.33%, the Nasdaq dropped 0.23%, and the Dow dipped 0.63%.

items.title: Jamie Dimon breaks with ‘idiots’ in Democratic Party, saying they ‘have big hearts and little brains’
items.description: "They do not understand how the real world works," said the JPMorgan Chase CEO. "Almost every single policy rolled out failed."

items.title: Exclusive: Crypto and stablecoin infrastructure startup Zerohash to raise $100 million at an almost $1 billion valuation
items.description: The company is the latest beneficiary of venture capital’s booming interest in stablecoins.
